[On Play] K.O. up to 1 of your opponent's Characters with a cost equal to or less than the total of your and your opponent's Life cards. Then, if you have 1 or less Life cards, add up to 1 card from the top of your deck to the top of your Life cards.
Disclaimer: This card was reprinted from the original set with changes to the artist credit (note the lack of pen symbol next to the artist name).

OP05-OP05-006 parallel.name: Koala (Reprint)
OP05-OP05-006 parallel.description:
[On Play] If your Leader has the [Revolutionary Army] type, give up to 1 of your opponent's Characters -3000 power during this turn.
Disclaimer: This card was reprinted from the original set with changes to the artist credit (note the lack of pen symbol next to the artist name).

OP01-OP01-121 parallel.name: Yamato (OP01-121) (Reprint)
OP01-OP01-121 parallel.description:
Also treat this card's name as [Kouzuki Oden] according to the rules.
[Double Attack] (This card deals 2 damage.)
[Banish] (When this card deals damage, the target card is trashed without activating its Trigger.)
Disclaimer: This card was reprinted from the original set with an additional security stamp on the bottom-left corner (note that this difference is not visible in official sample images).

P-P-055 alt2.name: Monkey.D.Luffy (P-055) (Reprint)
P-P-055 alt2.description:
[On Play] You may trash 2 cards from your hand: Your opponent places 1 of their Characters at the bottom of the owner's deck.
Disclaimer: This card was reprinted from the original set by removing the NOT FOR SALE on the border from the original print.

P-P-053 alt2.name: Nami (P-053) (Reprint)
P-P-053 alt2.description:
[On Play] If you have 3 or less cards in your hand, return up to 1 of your opponent's Characters with a cost of 3 or less to the owner's hand.
Disclaimer: This card was reprinted from the original set by removing the NOT FOR SALE on the border from the original print.
